      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SO HE THINKS (3) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 7 lengths at this track in a handy 34.18 beating Tiger Rocks. Boasts two wins from four starts out of this box. Form reads well for this. BLANKET GAME (7) has been in the minors the last two, the latest showing strong pace early but gathered in and finished a 5 length third over 390m Ballarat in 22.20. Well-placed to take this out. PAW VARNA (8) well back settling but did wind up strongly to finish 4th and beaten only 1.5 lengths (30.05) at this track. Key player if finds best. OLIVER KELTON (2) collected a minor prize last start and must be considered.",
